<img src="/mbimages/bsmembership.jpg" align="right"><span class="maintext"><h1>Membership Badge</h1>
<ol type=1>
	<li>Sing the Pambansang Awit and recite the Ako ay Pilipino.<p>
	<li>Recite the Scout Oath and Law, Scout Motto, and Slogan.<p>
	<li>Demonstrate how to execute the Scout Sign, Scout Salute, and Scout Handshake.<p>
	<li>Describe the Scout Badge.<p>
	<li>Earn and save enough money for our registration fee.<p>
	<li>Appear before your Troop in an investiture ceremony and commit yourself to the Scout Oath and Law.<p>
</ol></span><p><div class="fb-comments" data-href="http://www.mbcenter.org/htm/ranks.php?rnk=bsmembership" data-width="540\: data-numposts="10"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><!-- InstanceEndEditable --></td>
